1. *Vodom* je poplavio grad. (The city was flooded with water.)
2. Sprečavao je da voda uđe u kuću. (He prevented the water from entering the house.)
3. *Voda* je bila veoma hladna. (The water was very cold.)
4. Pije *vodu* svaki dan. (He drinks water every day.)
5. Pre četiri godine, poplavilo je mnogo sela *vodom*. (Four years ago, many villages were flooded with water.)
6. Čisti *vodu* u bazenu svaki dan. (He cleans the water in the pool every day.)